## Known Limitations

1. **Sequential execution only**: Stories run one at a time (no parallelization)
2. **Screenshot resolution required**: CI mode fails on mismatches (no auto-accept)
3. **Single browser context**: Each story runs in isolation (no state sharing)
4. **Fixed timeout**: 30-second timeout not configurable per action
5. **No iframe support**: Actions cannot target elements inside iframes
6. **No shadow DOM**: Elements in shadow DOM cannot be selected
7. **VS Code dependency**: Interactive resolution requires VS Code CLI for diff viewer (gracefully degrades if unavailable)
8. **Full page error screenshots**: May be very large for long pages

